title: Hour 1 - Jim Harbaugh and Jeff Passan (05-12-20)
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Jim Harbaugh and Jeff Passan (05-12-20)
description:
Michigan Football Head Coach Jim Harbaugh tells Dan that he is in agreement with college players being able to turn pro when ever they are ready. Dan goes over the odds for the NFL MVP and gives his pick.
